hadiths[26]{hadithnumber,text}:
4214,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne irada kiya ke ajmi (gair-arabi) baadshaahon ko khat likhen. to aap ko bataya gaya ke wo log mohar ke baghair khat nahin padhtey. to aapney chaandi ki anguthi banwaai jis mein ye kalimaat kanda (gude) they (Muhammad Rasulullah).
4215,"Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se mazkura baala hadees Esa bin Yunus ke ham-maani riwayat ki. is mein izafa hai : phir ye anguthi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haath mein rahi yahan tak ke aap ki wafat ho gaee, phir Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke haath mein rahi yahan tak ke unki wafat ho gaee , phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke haath mein rahi yahan tak ke unki wafat ho gaee , phir Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke haath mein aai. aur phir wo eik kunwen ke kinarey baithey they ke ittifaaq se us mein gir gaee. to unhoney Hukm diya aur uska sara pani nikala gaya. magar log isey talash nahi kar paey."
4216,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki anguthi chaandi ki thi aur uska nageena Habshi tha.
4217,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki anguthi sari ki sari chaandi ki thi , iska nageena bhi usi hi se tha."
4218,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke (pehley pehal) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne soney ki anguthi banwaai aur iska nageena hatheli ki janib rakhna shuru kiya aur is mein (Muhammad Rasulullah) ke alfaz kanda karwaaey to Sahaba ne bhi soney ke angoothiyaan banwaa lin. jab aapney ye dekha ke logon ne bhi (wesi hi angoothiyaan) banwaa li hain to aapney apni anguthi utaar phenki aur farmaya : ''main isey kabhi nahin pahnoon ga.'' phir aapney chaandi ki anguthi banwaai is mein bhi (Muhammad Rasulullah) ke alfaz naqsh karwaaey. aap ke baad ye anguthi Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne pahni, phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne pahni, phir unke baad Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne pahni yahan tak ke arees naami kunwen mein gir gaee. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Saiyedna Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se us waqt tak logon ne koi ikhtilaf nahin kiya yahan tak ke anguthi unke haath se gir gaee. (uskey baad ikhtilafat ne bhi sar utha liya .)"
4219,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne is khabar mein bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni anguthi mein (Muhammad Rasulullah) ke kalimaat kanda karwaaey aur farmaya : ''koi shakhs meri is anguthi ke naqsh ki tarah apni anguthi ka naqsh na banwaaey.'' phir hadees bayan ki.
4220,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki. (ibne-Umar ne) farmaya : (phir wo anguthi gum ho gaee) to logon ne usey talash kiya magar na pa sakey. to Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik (naee) anguthi banwaai jis mein (''Muhammad Rasulullah'') ke kalimaat naqsh karwaaey. chunanche wo isi se mohar kiya kartey they, ya isey pehna kartey they."
4221,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haath mein sirf eik din chaandi ki anguthi dekhi, to logon ne bhi banwaakar pehan lein. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo utaar phenki to logon ne bhi utaar phenki. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is riwayat ko Zohri se Ziyad bin Saad , Shuaib aur ibne Musafir ne riwayat kiya aur un sab ka bayan hai ke anguthi chaandi ki thi."
4222,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kiya kartey they ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko das baaten napasand thin (haram samajhtey they) zard rang ki murakkab khushbu yani khaluq, safed baalon ka (siyah) rang tabdeel kar dena, chadar ghaseet'taa, soney ki anguthi pehan'na, baghair moqa munasib ke zeenat ka izhar karna, gotiyon se khelna, sharae muawwizaat ke siwa doosrey dam jhaad,mankey koodiyaan waghaira latkana, ghair halal mein mani dalnaaur chhotey bachchey mein kharabi dalna, magar aap isey haram na kehtey they. (murad hai ayyaame raza'at mein bachchey ki maa se mubashrat karna. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko musnad riwayat kerney mein ehle-Basra munfarid (bilkul alag) hain. (والله أعلم)"
4223,"Janab Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya jabke usney peetal ki anguthi pahni hui thi. aapney us se farmaya : ''mujhey kya hai ke main tujh se buton ki boo paata hun?'' to usney wo anguthi utaar phenki. wo dobara aaya to lohey ki anguthi pehney hua tha, aapney farmaya : ''kya baat hai ke main tujh par dozakhiyon ka zewar dekhta hun?'' to usney wo bhi utaar phenki. Muhammad bin Abdul-Azeez ne ''Abdullah bin Muslim'' ka naam zikr nahin kiya (balke السلمی المروزی kaha) jabkey Hasan bin Ali ne ''السلمی المروزی'' nahin kaha (balke sirf Abdullah bin Muslim kaha)."
4224,Ayas bin Haris bin Muaiqeeb ne apney dada Muaiqeeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya. . . khayal rahey ke Ayas ke naana ka naam ''Abu Jubab'' hai. . unhoney kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki anguthi lohey ki thi jis par chaandi chadhaee gaee thi. kaha ke kabhi kabhi wo anguthi merey haath mein hoti thi. raawi ne kaha ke Hazrat Muaiqeeb (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki anguthi ke muhafiz they.
4225,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''ye dua kiya karo (اللهم اهدني وسددني) ''aey Allah ! mujhey hidayat dey aur sidha rakh.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hidayat'' mein raastey par sidha chalney aur ''saddaad'' mein teer ka nishaaney par lagney ke maani peshe-nazar rakha karo. phir shahadat wali ya darmiyani ungli ki taraf ishara kartey huey kaha ke aapney mujhey is mein ya is mein anguthi pehanney se mana farmaya. ye shak Aasim ko hua hai. . aur aapney mujhey (قسي) aur (ميثرة) se bhi mana farmaya. Hazrat Abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke ham ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke ''قسی'' se kya murad hai? unhoney kaha : is se murad naarangi ki tarah munaqqash (chhape huey) kapdey hain jo hamarey paas Shaam ya Misr se aatey they aur ''ميثرة'' se murad wo gudiyaan hain jo aurten apney shohron ke liye banati thin."
4226,Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne (marfooan) aur Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ne (mursalan) bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) anguthi daain haath mein pehna kartey they.
4227,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baeyn haath mein anguthi pehna kartey they aur uska nageena andar hatheli ki janib hua karta tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ibne Is'haq aur Usama bin Zaid ne Naafe se mazkura sanad se ye riwayat kiya : ''daeyn haath mein pehna kartey they.''
4228,Naafe bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) apni anguthi baeyn haath mein pehna kartey they.
4229,Muhammad bin Is'haq ne riwayat kiya kaha ke maine Salat bin Abdullah bin Nofal bin Abdul-Muttalib ko dekha ke unhoney apney daain haath ki chhanguliya mein anguthi pahni hui thi. maine kaha : ye kya? unhoney kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko dekha ke wo apni anguthi usi tarah pehna kartey they. aur uska nageena bahir ki taraf rakhtey they. aur Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke mutalliq khayal kiya jata hai ke wo kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni anguthi aisey hi pehna kartey they.
4230,Aamir bin Abdullah bin Zuber ka bayan hai ke hamari eik londi Zuber ki eik ladki ko Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan ley gaee. us ladki ke paon mein ghoongroo they. chunanche Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko kaat dala aur farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : '' her ghanti ke sath shaitan hota hai.''
4231,Bunaana Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Hayyaan Ansari ki londi bayan karti hai ke main Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan baithi hui thi ke unke paas eik ladki bheji gaee jisney aawaz daar ghoongroo pehney huey they. to unhoney kaha : isey merey paas mat lao warna uskey ghoongroo kaat dalo . unhoney bayan kiya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : ''jis ghar mein ghanti ho us mein farishtey dakhil nahin hotey.''
4232,"Abdur-Rehman bin Tarfa ne bayan kiya ke kulaab ki ladaai mein merey dada Arfaja bin As'ad ki naak kat gaee thi. to unhoney chaandi ki banwaai magar us mein boo pad gaee , to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen hukm diya to unhoney soney ki naak banwaa li."
4233,Yazid bin Harun aur Abu-Aasim dono ne kaha : hamein Abul-Ash'hab ne ba-waaste Abdur-Rehman bin Tarfa se unhoney Arfaja bin As'ad se mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. Yazid ne kaha ke maine Abul-Ash'hab se puchha : kya Abdur-Rehman bin Tarfa ne apney dada Arfaja ko paya tha? unhoney kaha : haan.
4234,Abdur-Rehman bin Tarfa ne Arfaja bin As'ad se unhoney apney walid se bayan kiya ke Arfaja ( . . . ki naak kat gaee thi) mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat kiya.
4235,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas Najashi ke yahan se kuchh zewrat aaye jo usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hadiya kiye they. un mein soney ki eik anguthi bhi thi jis ka nageena Habshi andaz ka tha. wo bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey lakdi se thaamaa aur aap us se aeraz kerney waley they. ya aapney isey apni ungliyon se pakda phir (apni nawaasi) Zenab ki beti Amaama dukhtar Abi al-Aas ko bulaya aur farmaya : ''beta ! ye tum pehan lo.''
4236,"Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney mehboob (bete, beti ya biwi waghaira) ko aag ka halqa pahanaanaa pasand karta ho to wo usey soney ka halqa pehna dey aur jisey pasand ho ke wo apney mehboob ke galey mein aag ka toq daley to wo usey soney ki hansli pehna dey aur jisey pasand ho ke wo apney mehboob ko aag ka kangan pahnaaey to wo usey soney ka kangan pehna dey. lekin tum log chaandi ikhtiyar karo aur us se dil bahlaao.''"
4237,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki bahan (Fatima ya Khaula) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey aurton ! kya tumhen zewar bananey ke liye chaandi kafi nahin hai. khabrdar ! jis aurat ne soney ka zewar pehna aur usey zahir kiya to usey usi se azab diya jaeyga''"
4238,Hazrat Asma binte Yazid (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aurat ne apney galey mein sona pehna qiyamat ke roz usey usi ki misl (jaisi) aag pahnaai jaeygi. aur jis aurat ne apney kaan mein soney ki baali pahni to qiyamat ke din usey usi ke misl aag ki baali pahnaai jaeygi.''
4239,Hazrat Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne cheeton ke chamdey ki guddi ya zeen posh par baithney se mana farmaya hai aur sona pehanney se bhi mana kiya hai siwaey iske ke maamuli ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abu-Qulaba ki Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat nahin hai.
